examples.en: Troops are advancing on the capital.
The storm is advancing towards the city.
The city fell to the advancing Russian armies.
The company tries to keep up with advancing technology.
I am proud of my contribution in advancing the project.
Soldiers were advancing on us from all points of the compass.
They laid down a barrage in front of the advancing troops.
A melancholy lesson of advancing years is the realization that you can't make old friends.
